  "statement": "\\text{Solve } \\quad \\sin x+\\sin 2x+\\sin 3x=\\cos x+\\cos 2x+\\cos 3x \\quad \\text{for } x\\in[0,2\\pi),\\ \\text{and count the solutions.}",
  "answer": "x=2k\\pi\\pm\\dfrac{2\\pi}{3}\\ \\text{ or }\\ x=\\dfrac{\\pi}{8}+\\dfrac{k\\pi}{2}; \\qquad \\boxed{6}\\ \\text{ solutions in } [0,2\\pi).",
